  "text": "Difficult to understand rendering logic\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.5.17\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nRun the provided demo\n\n### What is expected?\n\nRendering logic should be consistent\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\n<img width=\"1251\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1440a5dd-b7ff-49c6-b6b0-328ccfa1dd55\" />\n\nThe code logic is basically the same, why are the numbers displayed Asc and Desc?\n\n### System Info\n\n```shell\n\n```\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
